1767776585\" width=64 height=64 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2372330/extras/8921f95f309357fa23fd824e3cf8b262.apng?t=1767776585\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2372330/extras/8921f95f309357fa23fd824e3cf8b262.poster.avif?t=1767776585\" class=\"bb_img\" width=64 height=64 /></picture></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2372330/extras/d2c5c420eaf955f4837ca8c2d8494cac.avif?t=1767776585\" width=64 height=64 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Main Gameplay</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Master the mechanics of various weapons, including katanas, great katanas, spears, greatswords, chakrams, and more.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Standard attacks, charged attacks, precision charged attacks, counters, rising attacks, and other general combat moves.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Parry counter, blocking, dodging, perfect dodge, double jump, wall grab, ledge grab, dash glide, and other action elements.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2372330/extras/afe6903542190171ac1942363416ac47.poster.avif?t=1767776585\" width=800 height=448 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2372330/extras/afe6903542190171ac1942363416ac47.webm?t=1767776585\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2372330/extras/afe6903542190171ac1942363416ac47.mp4?t=1767776585\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In each challenge, choose different Tarot card entries to gain enhancement mechanics and corresponding attributes.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Reroll weapon enhancement entries in the shop, using limited resources and luck to pursue the maximum damage potential.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Consume \"Synthetic Blood\" to upgrade the out-of-game tech tree, continuously improving the character's basic abilities.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore and collect items on the map, give gifts to increase NPC affinity, and learn about the unique stories and anecdotes of the beautiful girls.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2372330/extras/44e748a46a64466f6af16fe4df5e3e1e.gif?t=1767776585\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2372330/extras/44e748a46a64466f6af16fe4df5e3e1e.poster.avif?t=1767776585\" class=\"bb_img\" /></picture></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2372330/extras/72d58c19e0de35b71cafdb57afa933a3.gif?t=1767776585\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2372330/extras/72d58c19e0de35b71cafdb57afa933a3.poster.avif?t=1767776585\" class=\"bb_img\" /></picture></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Game Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Nearly all characters and enemies are hand-drawn in pixel art, with complex and fluid animations.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A rich and diverse combat system featuring four basic classes and hundreds of Tarot card entries for endless combinations. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The EA version includes: 2 major stages and 5 sub-bosses (with hidden forms as well).</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Adorable pixel art girls: from base NPCs to powerful boss</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2372330/extras/4c99dd7af64b0c333db43445ca80f24e.poster.avif?t=1767776585\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2372330/extras/4c99dd7af64b0c333db43445ca80f24e.webm?t=1767776585\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2372330/extras/4c99dd7af64b0c333db43445ca80f24e.mp4?t=1767776585\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Thanks for your like and add to wishlist. This is the first game I've created and the first installment in Poetry of Blood series. I hope everyone will enjoy it!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2372330/extras/f5fdfab19d9dd26b6b04c98924132345.avif?t=1767776585\" width=616 height=352 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p>",
